                                            </span>

				
			        

        
    						<li class="b3">
			<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/reality-check-with-polly-curtis/2012/jan/12/internet-health#start-of-comments" class="content-comment-count" short-url="-p-34jg7">Comments (<span class="comment-count-val">&hellip;</span>)</a>
