 			<div class="section">
				<h1>Can you really be addicted to the internet? </h1>
		   		    									This article was published on
							<a href='http://www.guardian.co.uk/'>guardian.co.uk</a>
							at <time datetime="2012-01-12T00:00GMT" pubdate>11.41 GMT on Thursday 12 January 2012</time>. 
